      <title>Mashed Cover Ups: Social Media Sucks</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/posts/mashed-cover-ups/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Mar 2024 10:36:02 -0400</pubDate>
      <guid>//localhost:1313/posts/mashed-cover-ups/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;castgarden-video&#34;&gt;CastGarden Video&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe title=&#34;Mashed Cover Ups: Social Media Sucks&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;450&#34; src=&#34;https://cast.garden/videos/embed/b40c2f71-744d-4ed1-a21b-5cf1cb9ffd2d&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; allowfullscreen=&#34;&#34; sandbox=&#34;allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-popups&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;click-here-to-watch-this-video-on-torhttpcastgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddydonionwoevxtwgk418sbwu6yask5h&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://castgardn7yj746n7nyt3udot5orhpqfs36sl7rq2y3yd4su6ruuddyd.onion/w/oevXTWgk418sbwU6YAsk5H&#34;&gt;Click here to watch this video on Tor&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Originally published January 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&#xA;I&amp;rsquo;m not gonna lie. I been a little frustrated lately with social media. Mostly Twitter. It&amp;rsquo;s nothing but 2 sides saying anything and everything they can to piss each other off. The memes arent even funny anymore. Social media has run it&amp;rsquo;s course for me. I&amp;rsquo;m thinking that the only interactions I will have from now on will only be on Hive. If my posts on Dbuzz make it over to Twatter it&amp;rsquo;s because I actually remembered to push that button on Dbuzz.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
